  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Garment commissioning event at cut-and-sew facility.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries GS1 product master data plus product-level",
    "textile classification (textileCategory / apparelSubcategory / fabricType) — those",
    "describe the GTIN and are identical across every lot of this SKU, so they belong",
    "with the rest of the product card, not in ilmd (which is for lot-specific data).",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,textile=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/textile/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
